	Changelog:

	v3.0.3
	+ Fixed spell detector

	v3.0.2
	+ Fixed evading rectangular spells

	v3.0.1
	+ Fixed interaction between dodging and spell usage
	+ Made minor changes
	+ Optimized code

	v3.0
	+ Implemented new custom Pathfinding
	+ Added Neeko's spell data support
	+ Added some evade spells (Morgana E, Sivir E, Yasuo W)
	+ Added a lot of miscellaneous sliders in settings
	+ Improved missile tracking for all possible spells
	+ Extended danger value up to 5
	+ Updated spell data to patch 8.24
	+ Moved "Extra Radius" slider to Spell settings for each spell
	+ Optimized code

	v2.0.3
	+ Updated spell data for Ezreal
	+ Fixed detection of some spells

	v2.0.2
	+ Added selection of evade mode for circular spells
	+ Fixed drawings for extended safe position
	+ Fixed some bugs

	v2.0.1
	+ Fixed Summoner Flash usage
	+ Some minor changes in spell data

	v2.0
	+ Taken down Beta stage of Evade
	+ Added "Track Missiles" for tracking missiles (ex. Thresh Q)
	+ Added "Extend Safe Position" with slider
	+ Added "Limit Detection Range" with slider
	+ Added targeted spells to Spell Data
	+ Added dodging with Zhonya/Stopwatch for targeted spells
	+ Improved Pathfinding and moving to Safe Position
	+ Improved drawings for linear spells
	+ Fixed a lot of bugs

--]]

